Remaining Options to Choose From:
Option 5: Security & RBAC
ServiceAccounts with least privilege
Roles & RoleBindings for fine-grained access control
Network Policies to control pod-to-pod communication
Pod Security Standards (restricted, baseline, privileged)
Security Contexts for containers and pods
Option 6: Advanced Networking
Ingress Controllers (NGINX, Traefik, HAProxy)
Service Mesh (Istio, Linkerd, Consul)
API Gateways for external traffic management
Load Balancers and traffic splitting
Network Policies for micro-segmentation
Option 7: Backup & Disaster Recovery
Velero for cluster backup and restore
Multi-cluster management strategies
Disaster recovery procedures
Data backup and retention policies
Cross-region cluster replication
Option 8: Application Scaling & Performance
Horizontal Pod Autoscalers (HPA)
Vertical Pod Autoscalers (VPA)
Cluster Autoscaling for node management
Resource optimization and tuning
Performance monitoring and optimization
